    "Qualitative evaluation discussionThe capability of the BPLLM framework to respond appropriately to less structured and nuanced inquiries is also evaluated.",
    "Different questions are made to the BPLLM by a group of potential users involved in this experimentation.",
    "Figure 8 illustrates the same examples of the BPLLM's responses to such questions.",
    "The users, based on the obtained answers posit that the framework exhibits the ability to provide satisfactory responses promptly, thereby establishing its reliability for everyday usage.",
